  skos:altLabel "إمارة أندورا"@ar, "安道尔公国"@zh, "the Principality of Andorra"@en, "la Principauté d'Andorre"@fr, "el Principado de Andorra"@es, "Княжество Андорра"@ru ;
  skos:definition "全国划为7个行政区：安道尔城（Andorra la Vella）、卡尼略（Canillo）、马萨纳（Massana）、圣胡利娅～德洛里亚（Sant Julia de Loria）、恩坎普（Encamp）、莱塞斯卡尔德～恩戈尔达（Les Escaldes-Engordany）和奥尔迪诺（Ordino）。"@zh ;
  skos:note "It is incorrect to refer to the euro by nationality, for example as an Austrian euro or Belgian euro. However, one may refer to a country’s holdings of euro, for example euro (France) or euro (Germany).&nbsp;"@en, "DRAE: andorrano"@es ;
