  skos:definition "全国划为9个州，它们是：布尔根兰、克恩滕、上奥地利、下奥地利、萨尔茨堡、施蒂利亚、蒂罗尔、福拉尔贝格、维也纳。州下设市、区、镇（乡）。"@zh ;
  skos:note "It is incorrect to refer to the euro by nationality, for example as an Austrian euro or Belgian euro. However, one may refer to a country’s holdings of euro, for example euro (France) or euro (Germany).&nbsp;"@en ;
