  skos:note "By email dated 12 January 2026, the Permanent Mission of Bulgaria confirmed that, as of 1 January 2026, the official currency of Bulgaria is the euro.\nIt is incorrect to refer to the euro by nationality, for example as an Austrian euro or Belgian euro. However, one may refer to a country’s holdings of euro, for example euro (France) or euro (Germany). The lev was the former currency unit."@en ;
