  dct:contributor "gelena.ostroumova" ;
  skos:prefLabel "جمهورية أفريقيا الوسطى"@ar, "中非共和国"@zh, "Central African Republic (the)"@en, "République centrafricaine (la)"@fr, "República Centroafricana (la)"@es, "Центральноафриканская Республика"@ru ;
  skos:altLabel "جمهورية أفريقيا الوسطى"@ar, "中非共和国"@zh, "the Central African Republic"@en, "la République centrafricaine"@fr, "la República Centroafricana"@es, "Центральноафриканская Республика"@ru ;
  skos:definition "全国划分为16个省、１个直辖市（首都班吉），省以下设69个县。"@zh ;
  skos:note "*全称中非金融合作法郎，由中部非洲国家银行发行，是喀麦隆、中非共和国、乍得、刚果共和国、赤道几内亚、加蓬的法定货币。"@zh, "The CFA (Coopération financière en Afrique centrale) franc is the currency issued by the Bank of Central African States (BEAC). It is legal tender in Cameroon, the Central African Republic, Chad, the Congo, Equatorial Guinea and Gabon. Sometimes referred to by the acronym CAR in SC documents. <i>N.B.</i>: The adjective \"Central African\" applies to the Central African region, not the country, and should be avoided."@en, "Le sigle RCA est attesté dans les documents ONU."@fr, "Франк Африканского финансового сообщества — денежная единица ряда африканских государств."@ru ;
