  skos:definition "全国分为6个地区管理署和15个经济发展、交通和环境管理中心。"@zh ;
  skos:note "It is incorrect to refer to the euro by nationality, for example as an Austrian euro or Belgian euro. However, one may refer to a country’s holdings of euro, for example euro (France) or euro (Germany).&nbsp;"@en, "DRAE: finlandés"@es ;
