  skos:prefLabel "غابون"@ar, "加蓬"@zh, "Gabon"@en, "Gabon (le)"@fr, "Gabón (el)"@es, "Габон"@ru ;
  skos:altLabel "جمهورية الغابون"@ar, "加蓬共和国"@zh, "the Gabonese Republic"@en, "la République gabonaise"@fr, "la República Gabonesa"@es, "Габонская Республика"@ru ;
  skos:definition "全国划分为9个省，下辖49个州、27个专区、150个区、737个镇、2423个自然村。"@zh ;
  skos:note "*全称中非金融合作法郎，由中部非洲国家银行发行，是喀麦隆、中非共和国、乍得、刚果共和国、赤道几内亚、加蓬的法定货币。"@zh, "The CFA (Coopération financière en Afrique centrale) franc is the currency issued by the <xref onclick=\"javascript:openInternalReference(this)\" class=\"label label-inverse\" ulink=\"/display/record/UNHQ/Bank_of_Central_African_States/b2efc3f9-5ae9-463f-ac9f-e5ca131d5b31\">Bank of Central African States</xref> (BEAC). It is legal tender in Cameroon, Central African Republic, Chad, Congo, [The Republic of] Equatorial Guinea and Gabon."@en, "Франк Африканского финансового сообщества — денежная единица ряда африканских государств."@ru ;
