  skos:definition "全国划分为卢森堡、迪基希、格雷文马赫3个省，下辖12个专区、106个市镇。省长、市（镇）长由大公任命。"@zh ;
  skos:note "- It is incorrect to refer to the euro by nationality, for example as an Austrian euro or Belgian euro. However, one may refer to a country’s holdings of euro, for example euro (France) or euro (Germany). The franc was the former currency unit. \n- Variant forms of the name of the language include Luxembourgish, Letzeburgish, Letzeburgesch and Letzebuergesch."@en, "Dans la constitution (en français) de ce pays il est bien écrit: \"Grand-Duché DE Luxembourg\"."@fr ;
