  skos:prefLabel "مدغشقر"@ar, "马达加斯加"@zh, "Madagascar"@en, "Madagascar"@fr, "Madagascar"@es, "Мадагаскар"@ru ;
  skos:altLabel "جمهورية مدغشقر"@ar, "马达加斯加共和国"@zh, "the Republic of Madagascar"@en, "la République de Madagascar"@fr, "la República de Madagascar"@es, "Республика Мадагаскар"@ru ;
  skos:note "2005年取代原货币马达加斯加法郎。一个阿里亚里等于5个衣莱姆比郎甲。"@zh, "N.B.: The ariary is subdivided into five iraimbilanja and is one of only two non-decimal currencies currently circulating in the world (the other is the Mauritanian ouguiya).- The franc (ISO code MGF) was the currency until 1 January 2005 on which date it was replaced by the ariary at a rate of 5 francs to the ariary. The franc was divided into centimes."@en, "Variante ancienne du nom de la capitale : Tananarive. Depuis 2005, l'appellation \"ariary\" est redevenue la seule officielle pour désigner la monnaie de Madagascar remplaçant le franc malgache (FMG). L’ iraimbilanja est la seule subdivision de l’ariary et vaut 1/5 de celui-ci."@fr, "DRAE: malgache"@es ;
