  skos:note "- The second abbreviation of the currency unit may be used if necessary for clarification.- Majuro the location of the capital is an atoll. The capital is spread over the Delap Uliga and Darrit islets (DUD) at the eastern end of the atoll. This combination of islets is sometimes referred to by the acronym DUD. Delap is also seen spelled Dalap."@en, "La capitale est située sur trois ilôts (Dalap Uliga et Darrit) de l'atoll de Majuro."@fr ;
