  skos:note "--2006年10月7日，帕劳首都由科罗尔迁至梅莱凯奥克。"@zh, "- The second abbreviation of the currency unit may be used if necessary for clarification.<br>- In October 2006 Ngerulmud became the seat of government, replacing Koror as the capital city. This was confirmed in a communication dated 31 December 2024 from the Permanent Mission."@en, "Variantes hors ONU (pays et gentilé): Palau, palauan; Belau, bélauan. Les Palaos étant des îles, on emploiera le féminin."@fr, "DRAE: palauano"@es ;
