  skos:prefLabel "البرتغال"@ar, "葡萄牙"@zh, "Portugal"@en, "Portugal (le)"@fr, "Portugal"@es, "Португалия"@ru ;
  skos:altLabel "جمهورية البرتغال"@ar, "葡萄牙共和国"@zh, "the Portuguese Republic"@en, "la République portugaise"@fr, "la República Portuguesa"@es, "Португальская Республика"@ru ;
  skos:definition "全国设有18个大区，分别为：里斯本、波尔图、科英布拉、维亚纳堡、布拉加、雷阿尔城、布拉甘萨、瓜达、莱里亚、阿威罗、维塞乌、圣塔伦、埃武拉、法鲁、布朗库堡、波塔莱格雷、贝雅、塞图巴尔。另有亚速尔群岛和马德拉群岛2个自治区。"@zh ;
  skos:note "It is incorrect to refer to the euro by nationality, for example as an Austrian euro or Belgian euro. However, one may refer to a country’s holdings of euro, for example euro (France) or euro (Germany). The escudo was the former currency unit."@en, "Variante (gentilé capitale): Lisbonnais Lisboète"@fr, "DRAE: portugués, lisboeta"@es ;
