  skos:prefLabel "سانت كيتس ونيفس"@ar, "圣基茨和尼维斯"@zh, "Saint Kitts and Nevis"@en, "Saint-Kitts-et-Nevis"@fr, "Saint Kitts y Nevis"@es, "Сент-Китс и Невис"@ru ;
  skos:altLabel "سانت كيتس ونيفس"@ar, "圣基茨和尼维斯"@zh, "Saint Kitts and Nevis"@en, "Saint-Kitts-et-Nevis"@fr, "Saint Kitts y Nevis"@es, "Сент-Китс и Невис"@ru ;
  skos:note "The EC$ (East Caribbean dollar) is the legal tender in the following member countries of the East Caribbean Central Bank (ECCB): Antigua and Barbuda, Dominica, Grenada, Saint Kitts and Nevis, Saint Lucia and Saint Vincent and the Grenadines. Is referred to in other contexts -- but not at the UN -- as the Federation of Saint Christopher and Nevis. The State consists of two of the Leeward Islands. Basseterre is on the larger island of Saint Kitts."@en, "Variantes (hors ONU): Saint-Christophe-et-Niévès; Fédération de Saint-Christophe-et-Niévès"@fr, "Восточнокарибский доллар - валюта имеющая хождение в ряде стран входящих в Организацию Восточно-Карибских государств."@ru ;
