  skos:definition "全国分为3个省（即东方省、南方省和北方省）和西区。3个省之下设有12个行政区，行政区以下设149个酋长领地。"@zh ;
  skos:note "Portuguese name for the country: Serra Leoa (\"lion mountains\"). The country declared itself a republic on 19 April 1971."@en, "DRAE: sierraleonés"@es ;
