  skos:prefLabel "تركمانستان"@ar, "土库曼斯坦"@zh, "Turkmenistan"@en, "Turkménistan (le)"@fr, "Turkmenistán"@es, "Туркменистан"@ru ;
  skos:altLabel "تركمانستان"@ar, "土库曼斯坦"@zh, "Turkmenistan"@en, "le Turkménistan"@fr, "Turkmenistán"@es, "Туркменистан"@ru ;
  skos:definition "除首都阿什哈巴德外，全国划分成5个州、1个直辖市"@zh ;
  skos:note "The currency the manat replaced the Soviet ruble in 1993. In response to inflation a \"second manat\" was introduced in 2005 followed by a \"third manat\" or \"new manat\" on 1 January 2009. The banknotes have continued to just say \"manat\". After 2007 the International Standards Organization (ISO) changed the currency code from TMM for the pre-2007 manat to TMT for the new(er) manat."@en, "Variante (capitale): Achkhabad (forme russe)"@fr, "DRAE: turcomano"@es ;
